headline: S&P Global (SPGI) Traded Lower on Lowered Guidance
summary: Brown Advisory, an investment management company, released its “Brown Advisory Large-Cap Growth Strategy” second-quarter 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. The Brown Advisory Large-Cap Growth strategy has shown resilience this year amid heightened volatility, protecting investor capital during market declines and participating in the strong rebound since early April. headline: S&P Global Ratings affirmed Oma Savings Bank Plc's credit rating and changed outlook to negative
summary: OMA SAVINGS BANK PLC STOCK EXCHANGE RELEASE 10 SEPTEMBER 2025 AT 1.25 P.M.
